posed to update the password on every login, it doesn't on my machine. if it works on other machines, i can help to find out what the problem is with my setup.\r\n\r\nhowever, i think that we have a design problem here. passwords should not only be updated when the user logs in the next time. i was trying to get ampache to work for about an hour, trying to disable ssl, three different clients, new passwords etc all without logging out and in again. the only answer i got from my clients was \"invalid login\". this cannot be intended behaviour. the same goes for newly created accounts.\r\n\r\nfurthermore, there is no mechanism to delete users from the table. even if a user is deleted, its entry in media_users is not. this is a security whole!","closed_by":{"login":"ingomueller-net","id":1036898,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e8006a2dd6446ae899f06fc2d2a83ff5?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fc61d9abd26b7cf0329a2f1c217ee585e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"e8006a2dd6446ae899f06fc2d2a83ff5","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net","html_url":"https://github.com/ingomueller-net","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ingomueller-net/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}